message.body: Hey! Looks like not any good movies playing that we haven't already seen...anything you interested in?
Hey! Glad you're feeling better :) Such a bummer you've been having migraines lately!
I know! I can't figure it out!
I'd be down for that Elaine stritch movie...I really wish there was a horror movie playing! That's what I'm in the mood for!
I know!!! No horror movies this time of year! Jeesh! What tmw is Elaine striych??
Later in the afternoon would be good! I need to do laundry and clean the house a bit.
Actually, the more I think about it the more I realize how much shit I need to do today! Before my sister comes Sunday! Wanna just get lunch?
Yeah that sounds great! Sarah is coming from NYC tmw and I need to do a lot too! Wanna do salads for lunch? Or Something in university city?
Oh nice! She coming for your bday? Wanna go to sweetgreen for lunch? A little late would be good for me...I'm doing some painting right now! Maybe 2?
Yeah!! 2 is good and I am craving some greens. Text me when you are ready!
Ok so I'm just finishing with this painting and gonna clean up! Then gotta put on some regular clothes!
Cool! I'm gonna unload the dishwasher and make the bed!
You can head over whenever! I'm ready!
Cool! I'm gonna leave in like 5 minutes!
Hey! I can't find the artificial tears, but I know I have some somewhere! I'll keep looking, but in the mean time clean his eye with a warm compress! :)
Thanks tess!! Maybe that will be all he needs!
